{"tid":761193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小米（1810-W）昨宣佈穩定價格期結束    半日跌3%","createTime":"2018-07-30T07:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T08:01:51.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f07dbff0018edd338b0ecf8816b66765d6f2afaa","tid":761193,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180730/large/1532926599_8963.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180730%2Flarge%2F1532926599_8963.jpg&h=ca3bbb73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小米（1810）昨宣佈，與全球發售有關的穩定價格期已於周六（28日）結束。小米今股價受壓，半日最企見18.32元，午收18.48元，跌2.9%，半日成交金額5.09億元。<br />\n<br />\n穩定價格期由公司遞交香港公開發售申請截止日期起計30日。穩定價格行動由摩根士丹利亞洲、其聯屬人士或代其行事的任何人士進行，期間行動包括國際包銷商於本月17日就合共3.27億股B類股份，按每股發售價17元，悉數行使超額配股權，以償還之前根據借股協議向Morningside China TMT Fund I,L.P.借入以補足國際發售超額分配的B類股份。"},{"pid":"320af012a29592b1486575d9fc27bf1fefbd3585","tid":761193,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:36:48.000Z","msg":"等睇人血饅頭"},{"pid":"75fb4a653015f78fe905637616899e37957e89fa","tid":761193,"uid":117947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:52:23.000Z","msg":"穩定期完左2星期後就可以暴升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2599d0d8d511d74cf7a04def33e3cb042f04f10","tid":761193,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T08:00:21.000Z","msg":"小米乜都無宣布，有日跌7%"},{"pid":"af6bfa62fbf3d3ed7a25dc2955b1d3f7244b1121","tid":761193,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T08:01:51.000Z","msg":"乞米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}